+  ASSERT_EQ(position, buffer_size / 2);

 Review comment:
   Interesting. I wouldn't expect `WriteAt` to change the internal position at all. I'd rather remove those lines from the test (and perhaps `WriteAt` to remove the seeking, which hopefully won't break anything :-)).

